{"type": "article", "id": 48879, "title": "Vice辞退两名高管，以及，钟小姐代言欧莱雅 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-04T03:44:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 46210, "name": "VICE"}, {"id": 41071, "name": "Alexa Chung"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 46775, "name": "狗年生肖"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 15623, "name": "Gosha Rubchinskiy"}, {"id": 1203, "name": "权力的游戏"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180104101638e6UP1dr8luDCOxFt.jpeg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/02/business/vice-media-executives-on-leave.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>性骚扰风波之后，Vice Media 辞退了两名高管</strong></a> | 去年年底，《纽约时报》撰文爆出文化媒体 Vice 涉及性骚扰，现任总裁 Andrew Creighton 涉嫌其中。根据《纽约时报》的最新消息，Vice 宣布辞退 Andrew Creighton 以及数字主管 Mike Germano。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/ralph-lauren-2018-game-plan-focus-china-digital-wholesale-improvements-11080191/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Ralph Lauren 2018 年将专注中国市场发展</strong></a> | Ralph Lauren 的首席执行官 Patrice Louvet 表示，中国市场将是品牌 2018 年的发展重心。将通过不断扩张门店，进一步发展电商，增加营销支出等方式，吸引新一代的消费者。Patrice Louvet 预计，今年的新开门店数量将增至 60 家，随着大中华区的业务规模不断扩大，5 年内该地区销售额将实现 1.7 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/alexa-chung-named-face-of-loreal-professionnel-11083633/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Alexa Chung 成欧莱雅专业美发产品全球代言人</strong></a> | 欧莱雅集团正式宣布，任命英国 IT Girl 鼻祖“钟小姐”Alexa Chung 成为旗下专业美发产品 L’Oréal Professionnel 的全球代言人。欧莱雅集团在周三发布的一份声明中称，身兼设计师、模特、作者等多重身份的 Alexa Chung 是最受欢迎的新一代时尚代表人物之一。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111414NEY4gdZDjuW95Hkh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2018-01-04/gosha-burberry/topics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Burberry 和 Gosha Rubchinskiy 的首个联名 2018ss 正式发布完整系列单品，将于 1 月 6 日 上架。 </a></p><p>去年六月，Gosha 在圣彼得堡发布 2018 春夏新品时，就曾展出过与 Burberry 合作的 8 件单品。可以看到的是，Burberry 的格纹元素还在，但经典风衣廓形变大了，带上了 Gosha 的街头风。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111738D8FWi4320OQkdYRJ.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.647273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111737KnoGp38dLaVJf4Ig.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111741u7Nik82tfmvKQTAI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111742ntZgFJPi3OVm2XL0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111742EIg0ZMlN2s7ikFLY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111735ryOYzp3NWIbdV1k6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111737WsaNdCnfzbVwJRtS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111738iOlqHg4d21Pt6xCz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111740fd63XS9m5TP2AWwi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801041117412yRLu7HFsKWShO0i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.designweek.co.uk/issues/1-7-january-2018/game-thrones-stamps-designed-royal-mail-gbh/\" rel=\"nofollow\">GBH 工作室为英国皇家邮政设计了一套《权力的游戏》邮票。</a>这套邮票共有 15 张，包括 10 张主要人物的大图，以及五张 mini 尺寸的邮票。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111816vW6VuJ0YsONUoHqj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.739000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111817WXj8Z4BcfPYoCwqy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.743000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111818WpCfR0rKsyEeAowV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.729000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111817B6qCUQtY7kGcez8I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.745000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801041118175ofxW4Pi7H8kOrgw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.503000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111817KBJbNRhL7nXmwA1c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.355000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801041118205KsNrcMTQq4o6WaJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.387000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>在去年的 2018 度假系列秀场上首次亮相的 <a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/1/prada-cloudbust-mesh-trainer-bianco-argento-rosso-black-white-cromo-rosa\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada Cloudbust 球鞋</a>最近又推出了四款新的配色，每双售价 690 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111852eULb97W45poz3q1g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666450\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111854RYZJrwT1pfU6NV2b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666169\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111851WmGdp2ihUAPO0f3t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666912\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111851KVCbUfX8SMQByD7l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667183\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/dior-homme-denim-spring-2018/#slide-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior Homme 2018 春季系列</a>看起来还不错，创意总监 Kris Van Assche 用“双面牛仔”技术重新诠释了品牌风格。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111917JgBrGiH5zTyLnoWK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111914sS5kXOum60xURM3F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111917ZfdwQrtiR4sSOa6E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111914irjBA2pCkXHslymL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801041119152BOrhobaYvUe9K0i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111916A48l2PkhxoYTuCmp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801041119165PpJiBsZWorR6VqL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111916eWlva8PgASupiG13.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>临近农历新年，来看看各大品牌的“狗年生肖”系列主题都有哪些单品： </p><p>Moschino 狗年限量五件套 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104111946KRH9rG0oxq2pvAwn.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.544000\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><p>LV 柴犬印花包包&amp;钥匙扣、</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801041119546v3dQTjtlCmkFgsq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.184000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104112005DUV6ie7tOkpRPa3X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.840000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Givenchy 新年新包装口红&amp;散粉 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104112020hcjGMr3K1JsC5qdB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104112023ITdSXQ9jfV048kcB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104112023JdzupiK37qSF4Y9t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.931333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104112024yCkiaxvP2YUdfSOb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.295337\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Dior 红绳 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180104112032LgtSqCO3Ix0BE5u4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.812000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Burberry</p>"}